headline: ALL Q2 Deep Dive: Transformation Drives Profitable Growth, Focus on Market Share Expansion
summary: Insurance giant Allstate (NYSE:ALL) missed Wall Street’s revenue expectations in Q2 CY2025, but sales rose 6% year on year to $16.63 billion. Its non-GAAP profit of $5.94 per share was 82.5% above analysts’ consensus estimates.
